high_descs: Go forward and face the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick the tomato up from the counter.
Turn around and face the sink to the left.
Put the tomato in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the tomato up again.
Go left and face the microwave above the stove.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato in a microwave.

high_descs: Walk forward to the tomato on the counter.
Pick up the tomato from the counter.
Turn around and walk forward to the sink on the left, then turn left and face the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Turn around, walk forward a few steps toward the dining table, then turn right and walk to the stove top.
Put the tomato in the microwave above the stove top, then close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned tomato in a microwave.

high_descs: Go straight to the counter in front of you.
Pick up the tomato from the counter.
Turn around and go forward, then turn left to go to the sink.
Clean the tomato in the sink.
Turn around and move forward, then turn right to go toward the stove, then look up at the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato in the microwave.
